              <span id="reviewTextContainer4228224654" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10650613357317300888">LOVED the beginning of this book, super engaging, adorable meet cute, pop ups of other Hathaways. But the last half of the book sort of fell apart. Reveals happened to late, miscommunication happened too long. But still such an enjoyable book. But not close to how much I loved the first two.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


